Q: How can we frame problems?
A: The way you frame a problem determines which tools and techniques you apply to it.

  Decision - yes or no answer

  Optimization - find the best answer

  Counting - how many solutions exist

  Search - find any valid solution (not necessarily best)

  Function - compute an output for every input

